    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2204830/extras/e4918915a5faf5c8288498729218f8a8.poster.avif?t=1678986256\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2204830/extras/e4918915a5faf5c8288498729218f8a8.webm?t=1678986256\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2204830/extras/e4918915a5faf5c8288498729218f8a8.mp4?t=1678986256\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Near-endless cities to conquer </h2>Generate as many cities as you care to battle for, whenever you want and however you want.<br>Let the generator set the city’s name or perhaps change it to your current location for a more memorable experience.<br>Gang territories will be allocated differently each time - play as the underdog and overthrow the big boys in charge of town, crush other weak gangs in your dominant grip, or square off against evenly matched opponents - the choice is yours.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2204830/extras/cb3ca2aab23a7bf60f6548734581c821.poster.avif?t=1678986256\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2204830/extras/cb3ca2aab23a7bf60f6548734581c821.webm?t=1678986256\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2204830/extras/cb3ca2aab23a7bf60f6548734581c821.mp4?t=1678986256\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Almost-unlimited procedurally-generated gangs </h2>Street gangs, Mafioso bosses, tracksuit-clad, balaclava-wearing cartels - fight against a near-unlimited number of procedurally-generated gangs, customise their names and colours, and take charge of your own.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2204830/extras/9d1f19558f46d06626c58d139d9e3187.poster.avif?t=1678986256\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2204830/extras/9d1f19558f46d06626c58d139d9e3187.webm?t=1678986256\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2204830/extras/9d1f19558f46d06626c58d139d9e3187.mp4?t=1678986256\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Turn-based FPS hybrid </h2>Recruit foot soldiers, businessmen, leaders and assassins - deploy them, and control them on the urban battlefield.<br>Success will not just be achieved on the battlefield - strategic positioning of your faction members is key to victory.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2204830/extras/8c7a18d01b3d541dbf90d6c36c441ae6.poster.avif?t=1678986256\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2204830/extras/8c7a18d01b3d541dbf90d6c36c441ae6.webm?t=1678986256\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2204830/extras/8c7a18d01b3d541dbf90d6c36c441ae6.mp4?t=1678986256\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Fight in first person </h2>Wield a wide variety of weapons in hardcore, brutal FPS combat as you square-off against your rivals.<br>Carefully weighted ragdolls combined with a dynamic gore system deliver a satisfying combat experience.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2204830/extras/0ca134605e7bb5790264c36b9a964165.poster.avif?t=1678986256\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2204830/extras/0ca134605e7bb5790264c36b9a964165.webm?t=1678986256\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2204830/extras/0ca134605e7bb5790264c36b9a964165.mp4?t=1678986256\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > A living, breathing world </h2>Immerse yourself in a procedurally-generated news system that reports on current events in your city, including gang warfare - news is generated as you play the game, fight battles, take (and inflict) casualties!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2204830/extras/3e779681e0508f52ffc4aedf4c16ba1d.poster.avif?t=1678986256\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2204830/extras/3e779681e0508f52ffc4aedf4c16ba1d.webm?t=1678986256\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2204830/extras/3e779681e0508f52ffc4aedf4c16ba1d.mp4?t=1678986256\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Gory, sandbox firefights </h2>Prefer gory, sandbox, NPC firefights? A dedicated “Shootout” mode is available where you can watch NPCs fight each other or jump into FPS combat whilst using cinematic controls to capture slow-motion gory deaths and blood spilling - there’s nothing more satisfying than turning on slow-motion whilst emptying a full magazine into your enemy!",
